      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i just wonder about the edge cases though. like, what about religious stuff or cultural things that might look \"unconventional\" to some execs? say, folks wearing hijabs or turbans, or maybe even certain types of facial hair? do they need to do anything specific to make sure they aren't seen as \"distracting\" or \"unprofessional\" in those high-stakes environments?",
